metadata.name: Adorable Kittycorns #1
metadata.description: The Adorable Kittycorn is an incredibly rare creature, rumored to be living in the undisturbed parts of the metaverse. The idea the Adorable Kittycorns is to have limited supply collection of all 1/1 AI generated legendaries. If you happen to collect one, consider yourself lucky, for your life will be filled with good luck and fortune.
